response.overview: Tara, Macca and Adam are three best friends from Campbelltown. On a day intended to be a celebration of new life, these teenagers make a decision that can never be undone.  A short australian drama - screened at Aesthetic Film Festival 2024 and Flickerfest International Short Film Festival 2024.
response.tagline: Tara, Macca and Adam are three best friends from Campbelltown. On a day intended to be a celebration of new life, these teenagers make a decision that can never be undone.
response.title: Bottleneck
